SCORING OPTIMIZATION
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

Priority order:
1. Problem Statement Alignment (AI-powered personalization)
2. Accessibility (WCAG 2.1 AA)
3. Code Quality (TypeScript strict, clean architecture)
